{"word":"G3504 - νεόφυτος - neóphytos - neh-of'-oo-tos - Novice","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νεόφυτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">neóphytos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">neh-of'-oo-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Novice</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நூதன - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"newly - planted"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3501 - νέος - néos - neh'-os/3501\">G3501</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5453 - φύω - phýō - foo'-o/5453\">G5453</a>; <i>newly planted</i>, that is, (figuratively) a <i>young convert</i> (&ldquo;neophyte&rdquo;): - novice.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3501/3501\">G3501</a>, <a href=\"#/G3502/3502\">G3502</a>, <a href=\"#/G3503/3503\">G3503</a>, <a href=\"#/G3504/3504\">G3504</a>, <a href=\"#/G3555/3555\">G3555</a>, <a href=\"#/G3556/3556\">G3556</a>"}]}